Package: EcoDiet
Type: Package
Title: Estimating a diet matrix from isotopic and stomachal data sources
Description: The goal of the package is to estimate trophic links and a diet matrix 
    from isotopic and stomachal data using a Bayesian Hierarchical Model. The package 
    relies on rjags to run a MCMC approximation of the different variables.
Version: 0.0.0.900
Authors@R: c(
